-long-de.toem.impulse.samples.ISamples.getStartUnits()=<b>public long getStartUnits()</b><br/>Returns the position of the first sample as a multiple of its domain base (e.g. domain base=1ms; units = 100; -> domain value = 100ms).<br/><b>Class: </b><a href='https://toem.de/images/toem/impulse/javadoc3.0/de/toem/impulse/samples/ISamples.html#getStartUnits-'>de.toem.impulse.samples.ISamples</a><br/><b>Parameters:</b><ul></ul><br/><b>Returns: </b>
